what is a connection pool?


this is a small saved group of already -open database connections 


for example 

without a pool ! 

Request comes in
open new database connection
run query
close connection

Next request comes in
open new database connection
run query
close connection







with a pool 


Request comes in
take connection A from the pool
run query
return connection A to the pool

Next request comes in
take connection A again
run query
return connection A to the pool



pool = reusable database connections waiting to be used again



